Incident.Summary: Possession and distribution of child pornography

IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: Focus of this supplement: Inital report for CyberTipline Report # 162853112 Attachments: National Center for Missing and Exploited Children CyberTipline Report Number 162853112. Comcast Communications Subpoena. Preservation request for Snapchat, INC. Narrative: On June 1, 2023 I, TFC Honsinger, of the Maryland State Police Salisbury Barrack assisted by the Criminal Enforcement Division received CyberTipline Report #162853112 from the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children (hereinafter referred to as NCMEC). CyberTipline Report #162853112 was generated by Snapchat, INC who reported on 05/27/2023 at 02:07:27 UTC that the below listed suspect uploaded child pornography to the internet. CyberTipline Report #162853112 reported the child pornography was uploaded by Snapchat Screen/User Name: blacktoothgri20 utilizing IP Address 73.180.233.168 which is registered to Comcast Cable Communications and geo-locates to Salisbury, Maryland. I reviewed the reported file provided by Snapchat, INC and confirmed that one (1) file did in-fact depict child pornography. The file is described as the following: Filename: blacktoothgri20-None-fae89025-ed00-54f1-84bd-b79bb36699de~5-e97907cec3.mp4 Description: One (1) video depicting a prepubescent female under the age of 16 (approximately 10 to 12 years of age) lying on her back nude from the waist down, wearing a dark blue shirt. In the video it was observed the prepubescent female had both legs lifted in the air and a male suspect holding her left leg. In the video the male suspect is observed engaging in anal sex with the prepubescent female. Comcast Cable Communications: On June 1, 2023 I, TFC Honsinger, of the Maryland State Police Salisbury Barrack, assisted by the Criminal Enforcement Division Eastern Region authored a records subpoena to Comcast Cable Communications in reference to IP Addresses 73.180.233.168 utilized on 05-27-2023 at 02:07:27 UTC and 73.180.233.168 utilized on 05-27-2023 at 07:37:11 UTC. Requesting subscriber information/ records to include full name(s), addresses (billing and physical), associated telephone numbers, email addresses, etc. associated with the previously listed IP Address. The subpoena was signed by the Wicomico County States Attorneys Office, and served on Comcast Cable Communications via their law enforcement portal. Snapchat, INC: On June 1, 2023 I, TFC Honsinger, of the Maryland State Police Salisbury Barrack, assisted by the Criminal Enforcement Division Eastern Region authored a preservation request for the account associated with Screen/User Name: blacktoothgri20 requesting the following be preserved: Account Information: All user provided information to include: names, email addresses, date /time of account registration, date/time files created/uploaded, date/time files deleted, type of account, payment details, IP address recorded for account logins, last-seen IP address of devices linked to the account and any mobile device information and all Snapchat created account notes or other records associated with the listed account. Snapchat content: All current live and deleted user content associated with the listed Snapchat account and; pictures and videos being stored, shared links created by the user, date time files created/uploaded and date and time files deleted from May 26, 2023 through June 1, 2023 for the following Snapchat account. The preservation letter was served on Snapchat on June 1, 2023 at approximately 1411 hours (2:11 p.m.). Case open, investigation continuing.

Focus of Supplemental Report: Search Warrant Service on Snapchat Attachments: Signed Search and Seizure Warrant Signed by The Honorable Karen M. Dean Narrative: On June 2, 2023, I TFC Honsinger #6841, of the Maryland State Police Salisbury Barrack assisted by the Criminal Enforcement Division authored a search and seizure warrant for Snapchat, INC. The search and seizure warrant was signed by the Honorable Judge Karen M. Dean on June 2, 2023 and served on Snapchat on June 2, 2023 at approximately 1115 hours (11:15 a.m.). On June 9, 2023 I completed the MSP 98 and MSP 98a and they were submitted to the Honorable Judge Karen M. Dean for her signature. On June 9, 2023 at approximately 1203 hours (12:03 pm) the Honorable Judge Dean signed and returned the MSP 98 and MSP 98a. Case open, investigation continuing.

Focus of Supplemental Report: Comcast Subpoena Response Narrative: On 06/13/2023 I, TFC Matthew T. IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeTitle: Snapchat Search and Seizure Warrant Results
IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: Focus of Supplemental Report: Snapchat search and seizure warrant results. Attachments: 1. MSP 67 for Snapchat evidence placed into property. Narrative: On June 19,2023 I, TFC Honsinger #6841, of the Maryland State Police Salisbury Barrack assisted by the Criminal Enforcement Division received the results from the Snapchat, INC search and seizure warrant. The search and seizure warrant was signed by the Honorable Judge Karen M. Dean on June 2, 2023 and served on Snapchat, INC on June 2, 2023 at approximately 1115 hours (11:15 am). On June 20, 2023, I was able to conduct a review of the content provided by Snapchat, INC. During my review of the content I located two video file: Filename: .mp4 Description: One (1) video depicting a prepubescent female under the age of 16 (approximately 10 to 12 years of age) lying on her back nude from the waist down, wearing a dark blue shirt. In the video it was observed the prepubescent female had both legs lifted in the air and a male suspect holding her left leg. In the video the male suspect is observed engaging in anal sex with the prepubescent female. Filename: chat~media_v4~2023-05-27-02-07-27UTC~blacktoothgri20~phm~fae89025-ed00-54f1-84bd-b79bb36699de-5~v4 Description: One (1) video depicting a prepubescent female under the age of 16 (approximately 10 to 12 years of age) lying on her back nude from the waist down, wearing a dark blue shirt. In the video it was observed the prepubescent female had both legs lifted in the air and a male suspect holding her left leg. In the video the male suspect is observed engaging in anal sex with the prepubescent female. These videos are the same videos which were reported by the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children in Cybertipline Report 162853112. The evidence received from Snapchat were stored on a Compact Disc (CD), a MSP 67 chain of custody was completed, and the evidence was placed into property as per Maryland State Police Policy. Case open, investigation continuing.

Focus of Supplemental Report: Case Reassignment Narrative: Due to the fact that Trooper First Class Honsinger, will be returning to his assignment at the Salisbury Barrack and Senior Trooper Garrett Dick, #6158 has been overseeing this investigation the case will be reassigned to S/T Dick for further investigation. Case open, investigation continuing.

Focus of Supplemental Report: Administrative Closure Narrative: As of todays date, I S/T Garrett Dick #6158 of the Maryland State Police Criminal Enforcement Division Eastern Region will be closing this case administratively, after review of the reported content, I determined that a criminal investigation is not warranted at this time; however the cyber tip referral was administratively documented. Case CLOSED.
